ars his name. English explorer Henry Hudson sailed into the river that now bears his name. Hudson sailed for the Dutch East India Company in search of the Northwest Passage, a water route linking the Atlantic and Pacific Oceans, when he sailed up the present-day Hudson River.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1356711,"age":82,"year":"1642","julianDay":2320789,"description":"Curacao became a colony of the Netherlands.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1356712,"age":88,"year":"1648","julianDay":2322980,"description":"End of Eighty Years' War with Spain.","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Mary Jans Lijsken was born about 1560, in Amsterdam, Holland, Netherlands as the daughter of Griet Van Den Lijsken. She had at least 1 daughter with Willem Cornelis Rudolph Janz. She died in 1651, in Friesland, Netherlands, at the age of 92."},"et":{"abt 1560–1651":"umbes 1560–1651","1560–1651":"1560–1651","1564–1630":"1564–1630","1598–1651":"1598–1651","–Male":"Surnud","1572":"1572","1560":"1560","abt 1560":"umbes 1560","1600":"1600","1642":"1642","1598":"1598","1630":"1630","1564":"1564","08 Dec 1598":"8. detsember 1598","1651":"1651","1584":"1584","1573":"1573","1609":"1609","about 1630":"umbes 1630","1648":"1648","Leiden, South Holland, Netherlands":"Leiden, Zuid-Holland, Madalmaad","Amsterdam, Holland, Netherlands":"Amsterdam, Holland, Madalmaad","Leuwarden, Friesland, Netherlands":"Friesland, Madalmaad","Haarlem, North Holland, Netherlands":"Haarlem, Noord-Holland, Madalmaad","Leuwarden,Friesland, Netherlands":"Friesland, Madalmaad"},"fi":{"abt 1560–1651":"noin 1560–1651","1560–1651":"1560–1651","1564–1630":"1564–1630","1598–1651":"1598–1651","–Male":"Kuollut","1572":"1572","1560":"1560","abt 1560":"noin 1560","1600":"1600","1642":"1642","1598":"1598","1630":"1630","1564":"1564","08 Dec 1598":"8. joulukuuta 1598","1651":"1651","1584":"1584","1573":"1573","1609":"1609","about 1630":"noin 1630","1648":"1648","Leiden, South Holland, Netherlands":"Leiden, Zuid-Holland, Alankomaat","Ams